  "2168810": {
    "name": "志怪者",
    "steam_appid": 2168810,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "这是一场属于冒险者的游戏。“狂梦”危机席卷人类，作为调查员的你需要潜入梦中，通过调查与抉择、骰点与战斗，在迷局中探险解谜，挖掘隐藏的真相，拯救深陷危机的狂梦患者。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/8b88fd051914a50565ed5c7f091a22e3.poster.avif?t=1705297849\" width=628 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/8b88fd051914a50565ed5c7f091a22e3.webm?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/8b88fd051914a50565ed5c7f091a22e3.mp4?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >颠覆跑团</h2>DBG融合肉鸽元素，随机地图、百变卡组，构筑你的独属流派。潜入变幻莫测无限轮回大厦，遭遇叫魂、赶尸、鬼新娘等中式恐怖民俗事件。参加恐怖游戏综艺秀，在美式大庄园进行惊心动魄玩家对决，附身者将会是谁？经典跑团规则之下全新体验！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/c8b25d6f25d165b05374f831a0de6655.poster.avif?t=1705297849\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/c8b25d6f25d165b05374f831a0de6655.webm?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/c8b25d6f25d165b05374f831a0de6655.mp4?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样剧本</h2>【丰富主题】灾难逃生、民俗调查、秘境探险、悬疑推理……多主题剧本随开随玩，沉浸式线上密室剧场体验。<br>【强随机性】剧本引入随机场景、遭遇、推理剧情元素，复玩性更强。隐藏物品和线索导向意想不到的真相，需要你勇于发现，大胆尝试，出奇制胜。<br>【多分支结局】每个多人剧本拥有5个以上分支结局，你的选择决定剧情走向，故事由你书写。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/d7301b59cd46906a6f30a42692826356.poster.avif?t=1705297849\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/d7301b59cd46906a6f30a42692826356.webm?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/d7301b59cd46906a6f30a42692826356.mp4?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >命运骰点</h2>骰点检定，决定命运！承袭跑团精髓，游戏走向由随机骰点决定，险中求胜还是意外翻车？善待你的骰娘，骰娘也会善待你！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/acded24f573361f645f7c5784927b2f1.poster.avif?t=1705297849\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/acded24f573361f645f7c5784927b2f1.webm?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/acded24f573361f645f7c5784927b2f1.mp4?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >卡牌策略 </h2>超150张卡牌任你自由搭配，围绕调查员的专长与流派构筑卡组，合理运用角色特性，基于卡牌进行探索与战斗，探索不同的可能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/c36108cb04381cedef22d5f02ff05208.poster.avif?t=1705297849\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/c36108cb04381cedef22d5f02ff05208.webm?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/c36108cb04381cedef22d5f02ff05208.mp4?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢乐互动</h2>1~4人自由组队，鞭笞“受虐狂”，恐吓“惊吓癖”，“疯狂模式”多人互动趣味连连。“献祭队友” 吸引火力，友聚还是友尽由你选择......<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/77def388ba88976eedb72ec49ef45791.poster.avif?t=1705297849\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/77def388ba88976eedb72ec49ef45791.webm?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/77def388ba88976eedb72ec49ef45791.mp4?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为传奇调查员</h2>扮演能力各异的调查员，运用他们的专长解决冒险中的难题。每个调查员的背后也许都藏着不为人知的过往，而你喜欢的NPC，也可能成为被解锁的角色。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/90a69faf29fec4d051f0eb89ca6331d9.poster.avif?t=1705297849\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/90a69faf29fec4d051f0eb89ca6331d9.webm?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/90a69faf29fec4d051f0eb89ca6331d9.mp4?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
